FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common queries about our food delivery app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How do I place an order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Simply browse restaurants, select your items, add them to your cart, and proceed to checkout. Choose your delivery address and payment method, then confirm your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: What payment methods do you accept?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We accept credit/debit cards, digital wallets, and cash on delivery in most areas. Available payment options will be displayed at checkout.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Delivery times vary depending on the restaurant's location and your delivery address. You'll see an estimated delivery time before placing your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, you can track your order in real-time through our app. You'll receive notifications about order confirmation, preparation, and when your delivery is on its way.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if there's an issue with my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: If you encounter any problems with your order, please contact our customer support team through the app or website. We're here to help resolve any issues promptly.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food delivery app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants and delivery drivers. Simply browse menus, place your order, and track your food in real-time until it arrives at your doorstep.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Delivery fees vary based on the restaurant's distance and current demand. The exact fee will be displayed before you confirm your order, ensuring full transparency.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I schedule orders in advance?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes! You can schedule orders up to 7 days in advance. This feature is perfect for planning meals or ensuring you have food ready for a specific time or event.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How can I contact customer support?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: You can reach our customer support team 24/7 through the app's help center, via email, or by phone. We're always here to assist you with any questions or concerns about your order.
